      "Long work hours and frequent business dinners had affected my weight and digestion. Rohan structured a plan that fit my schedule without drastic changes. I've lost fat steadily and feel more energetic during the day.",
    name: "Arjun R.",
    location: "Dubai, UAE",
  },
  {
    quote:
      "I had issues with acidity and late-night cravings. Rohan focused on meal timing and balance rather than restriction. The improvement in digestion and sleep has been noticeable.",
